## 6. TRENDING AUR REAL-TIME TREND ANALYSIS

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Trending** page: hashtag/keyword trends, growth velocity, opportunity score
- **Discover trends** API se rising/peak/declining trends milte hain
- Hashtag generator trending topics use karta hai taaki suggestions relevant rahein

### APIs
- `GET /api/trends/discover` – Trends list
- `GET /api/trending` – Trending topics

### Fayde
- Trending topics use karke content zyada discover ho sakta hai; hashtags up-to-date rehte hain.

---

## 7. BEST POSTING TIME PREDICTIONS

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Posting Time** page par platform (YouTube, Facebook, Instagram, TikTok) ke hisaab se **heatmap** (day × hour) aur **best day + hour** dikhta hai
- Category (comedy, education, music, etc.) ke hisaab se time adjust ho sakta hai

### APIs
- `GET /api/posting-time` – Heatmap + best time

### Fayde
- Sahi time post karke views aur engagement badhane mein madad.

