## 10. CONTENT CALENDAR AUR SCHEDULING

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Content Calendar** page par din aur platform ke hisaab se posts plan kiye ja sakte hain
- Schedule APIs se calendar data aur post schedule manage hota hai

### APIs
- `GET /api/schedule/calendar`
- `POST /api/schedule/post`

