## 13. TEAM COLLABORATION (ENTERPRISE)

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- Enterprise user **team** bana sakta hai (max 10 members)
- Owner **invite link** generate karta hai; doosre users link se **join** karte hain
- Team list: `GET /api/team`; create: `POST /api/team`; join: `POST /api/team/join` (token)

### Fayde
