## 15. API ACCESS (PUBLIC API)

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Settings** se user **API key** create karta hai (vb_xxx…); key sirf ek baar dikhai deti hai
- Kisi bhi request mein header: **X-API-Key: your_key**
- **Public endpoint:** `GET /api/public/v1/usage` – usage + subscription (API key se auth)

### APIs
- `GET /api/settings/api-keys` – List keys
- `POST /api/settings/api-keys` – Create key
- `DELETE /api/settings/api-keys?id=...` – Delete key
- `GET /api/public/v1/usage` – Usage (X-API-Key)

### Fayde
- Apne tools/apps se usage aur plan check kar sakte ho; automation possible.

---

## 16. CUSTOM INTEGRATIONS (WEBHOOKS)

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Settings** mein **Webhook URL** save karte ho
- Jab bhi koi video **analysis complete** hoti hai, tumhari URL par **POST** request jati hai – event name + payload (videoId, title, viralProbability, platform, etc.)

### APIs
- `GET /api/settings/webhook` – Current webhook
- `POST /api/settings/webhook` – Save URL

### Fayde
- External systems (CRM, Slack, custom dashboard) ko real-time event mil sakte hain; integrations easy.

